msgid "Panel"
msgstr "面板"

#: ../../manual/grease_pencil/modes/draw/tool_settings/draw.rst:11
msgid ":menuselection:`Toolbar --> Tools --> Draw Tools --> Draw`"
msgstr ":menuselection:`工具栏 --> 工具 --> 绘制工具 --> 自由线`"

#: ../../manual/grease_pencil/modes/draw/tool_settings/draw.rst:13
msgid "The Draw tool allows you to draw free-hand strokes."
msgstr "这个绘制工具允许你自由绘制。"

#: ../../manual/grease_pencil/modes/draw/tool_settings/draw.rst:17
msgid "Usage"
msgstr "使用方法"

#: ../../manual/grease_pencil/modes/draw/tool_settings/draw.rst:20
msgid "Selecting a Brush and Material"
msgstr "选择笔刷和材质"

#: ../../manual/grease_pencil/modes/draw/tool_settings/draw.rst:22
msgid ""
"In the Tool Settings select the brush and material to use with the tool. "
"The Draw tool uses *Draw Brush* types. See :ref:`grease-pencil-draw-"
"common-options` for more information."
msgstr ""
"在工具设置中，选择此工具使用的笔刷和材质。此工具使用 *绘制笔刷* 类型。详"
"见 :ref:`grease-pencil-draw-common-options`。"

#: ../../manual/grease_pencil/modes/draw/tool_settings/draw.rst:28
msgid "Common Brush Options"
msgstr "常用笔刷选项"

#: ../../manual/grease_pencil/modes/draw/tool_settings/draw.rst:30
msgid ""
"You can also configure the brush main settings exposed on the Tool "
"Settings for convenience. For the draw brushes configuration and settings "
"see: :doc:`Draw Brush </grease_pencil/modes/draw/tool_settings/brushes/"
"draw_brush>`."
msgstr ""
"你可以在工具设置中方便地更改笔刷配置。具体的笔刷配置和设置请参考 :doc:`绘"
"制笔刷 </grease_pencil/modes/draw/tool_settings/brushes/draw_brush>`。"

#: ../../manual/grease_pencil/modes/draw/tool_settings/draw.rst:36
msgid "Free-hand Drawing"
msgstr "自由绘制"

#: ../../manual/grease_pencil/modes/draw/tool_settings/draw.rst:38
msgid ""
"Click and hold :kbd:`LMB` or use the pen tip to make free-hand drawing on "
"the viewport."
msgstr "点按 :kbd:`LMB` 或 :kbd:`Pen` 在视角绘制自由线。"

#: ../../manual/grease_pencil/modes/draw/tool_settings/draw.rst:40
msgid "Drawing free-hand strokes."
msgstr "自由绘制的笔画。"

#: ../../manual/grease_pencil/modes/draw/tool_settings/draw.rst:53
msgid "Stabilizer"
msgstr "稳定"

#: ../../manual/grease_pencil/modes/draw/tool_settings/draw.rst:55
msgid ""
":kbd:`Shift-LMB` toggle the use of :ref:`Stabilizer <grease-pencil-draw-"
"brushes-stabilizer>` on the brush to have more control while drawing and "
"obtain smoother lines."
msgstr ""
"使用 :kbd:`Shift-LMB` 或笔刷选项中的 :ref:`稳定 <grease-pencil-draw-"
"brushes-stabilizer>` ，可以控制画笔获得更平滑的线条。"

#: ../../manual/grease_pencil/modes/draw/tool_settings/draw.rst:58
msgid "Drawing strokes using Stabilizer."
msgstr "开启稳定绘制的笔画。"

#: ../../manual/grease_pencil/modes/draw/tool_settings/draw.rst:71
msgid "Straight Lines"
msgstr "直线"

#: ../../manual/grease_pencil/modes/draw/tool_settings/draw.rst:73
msgid ""
":kbd:`Alt-LMB` Constrains the drawing of the strokes to horizontal or "
"vertical straight lines."
msgstr ":kbd:`Alt-LMB` 限制画出水平或竖直的线条。"

#: ../../manual/grease_pencil/modes/draw/tool_settings/draw.rst:77
msgid "Switching to the Erase Tool"
msgstr "切换擦除工具"

#: ../../manual/grease_pencil/modes/draw/tool_settings/draw.rst:79
msgid ""
":kbd:`Ctrl-LMB` changes temporally to the active erase tool. see :doc:"
"`Erase Tool </grease_pencil/modes/draw/tool_settings/erase>` for more "
"information."
msgstr ""
":kbd:`Ctrl-LMB` 暂时激活擦除工具。详见 :doc:`擦除工具 </grease_pencil/"
"modes/draw/tool_settings/erase>`。"

#: ../../manual/grease_pencil/modes/draw/tool_settings/draw.rst:82
msgid ""
"You can also use :kbd:`B` to delete all the points in the selected "
"drawing area."
msgstr "你可以使用 :kbd:`B` 框选，删除选中区域的所有点。"
